8/07/3.-buyer-funds-transaction.jpg" class="vc_single_image-img attachment-full" alt="3. buyer funds transaction" /></div></figure></div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-9"><div class="vc_column-inner "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><h4>3. Buyer Funds Transaction</h4><p>The buyer funds the transaction into KingsTrust<sup>®’</sup>s escrow account via wire transfer. Both parties are notified that all funds are in escrow and that it is safe to complete the transaction.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="process-step-4" class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1532102266597"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-3"><div class="vc_column-inner "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div  class="wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_left  vc_custom_1532102543523"><figure class="wpb_wrapper vc_figure"><div class="vc_single_image-wrapper   vc_box_border_grey"><img width="193" height="132" src="../wp-content/uploads/2018/07/4.-seller-delivers-goods-and-requests-payment.jpg" class="vc_single_image-img attachment-full" alt="4. seller delivers goods and requests payment" /></div></figure></div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-9"><div class="vc_column-inner "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><h4>4. Seller Delivers Goods &amp; Requests Payment</h4><p>Once the transaction details have been satisfied, the seller will request a release of funds. They may also upload useful documents.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="process-step-5" class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1532102400417"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-3"><div class="vc_column-inner "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div  class="wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_left  vc_custom_1532102547913"><figure class="wpb_wrapper vc_figure"><div class="vc_single_image-wrapper   vc_box_border_grey"><img width="193" height="132" src="../wp-content/uploads/2018/07/5.-buyer-verifies-delivery-of-goods.jpg" class="vc_single_image-img attachment-full" alt="5. buyer verifies delivery of goods" /></div></figure></div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-9"><div class="vc_column-inner "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><h4>5. Buyer Verifies Delivery of Goods</h4><p>The buyer confirms that the transaction has been completed as agreed and approves the release of funds.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="process-step-6" class="vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1532102411979"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-3"><div class="vc_column-inner "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div  class="wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_left  vc_custom_1532102552627"><figure class="wpb_wrapper vc_figure"><div class="vc_single_image-wrapper   vc_box_border_grey"><img width="193" height="132" src="../wp-content/uploads/2018/07/6.-releases-funds-to-seller.jpg" class="vc_single_image-img attachment-full" alt="6. releases funds to seller" /></div></figure></div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-9"><div class="vc_column-inner "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><h4>6. KingsTrust<sup>®</sup> Releases Funds to Seller</h4><p>KingsTrust® releases the funds directly into the seller’s bank account, and the transaction is closed.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section  class="wpb_row main_row  no-seperator" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:40px;"><div class="row-inner"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="separator_simple" style="border-color:#e2e2